-- Ex-Rio CEO Tom Albanese Joins Board of Canada’s Franco-Nevada
-- B y   L i e z e l   H i l l
-- 2013-08-07T21:45:14Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-08-07/ex-rio-ceo-tom-albanese-joins-board-of-canada-s-franco-nevada.html
Tom Albanese, who was chief executive
officer of Rio Tinto Group until he left in January, was
appointed to the board of Canada’s  Franco-Nevada Corp. (FNV)   Franco-Nevada, which gets its income from gold-mining and
other royalties, commented today in its second-quarter earnings
statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
